        "# 06 Grassed Waterway\n",
        "\n",
        "## Location\n",
        "\n",
        "The location of the grassed waterway is defined in **\\[reach_bmp\\]**\n",
        "section using **grass_waterway_shapefile**. One example is given below.\n",
        "The shapefile must be **polyline** type.\n",
        "\n",
        "*\\[reach_bmp\\]*\n",
        "\n",
        "*grass_waterway_shapefile = GWW.shp*"
